# Vercel reads this file relative to a project's Root Directory.
#
# This repo deploys as TWO Vercel projects:
#   * aec-platform-web   — Root Directory = apps/web
#                          (this .vercelignore is NOT read by that project,
#                           since it's outside apps/web)
#   * aec-platform-api   — Root Directory = ./
#                          (this .vercelignore IS read)
#
# The API project deploys the FastAPI via api/index.py as a Python
# serverless function. We exclude the heavyweight Next.js + UI source
# trees from its build context to stay under Vercel's 50MB function
# bundle limit on the Hobby tier.

apps/web/
packages/ui/
packages/types/
node_modules/
.next/

# Local dev artefacts that should never reach either deploy.
*.log
.DS_Store
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
